databaseQueries.query: SELECT `users`.*, (SELECT COUNT(winner_id) FROM matches WHERE player1_id = users.id OR player2_id = users.id) AS matches_played, (SELECT COUNT(winner_id) FROM matches WHERE winner_id = users.id) AS matches_won, (SELECT SUM(player1_sets_won) FROM matches WHERE player1_id = users.id) + (SELECT SUM(player2_sets_won) FROM matches WHERE player2_id = users.id) AS sets_won FROM `users` ORDER BY `matches_won` DESC
